<h2>Properties</h2>
	<p>The Properties Manager allows the adjustment of several visual, behavioural, and technical details of a course. Options include the course title and description, release date, the default language used, exporting behaviour, course access level, copyright, and course icon. The Properties Manager is also where to <a href="delete_course.php">delete the course</a>. Additional properties are managed by the ATutor administrator including upload file size limitations and space limitations for a course. Contact an ATutor administrator if these properties need to be changed.</p>

